Licence: GPLV2

Dependency: matplotlib, pygame, numpy

Currently available methods inside source/lib/odak.py

- Method for Fresnel and Fraunhofer diffractions
- Method for creating apertures such as circular, rectangular, slits and two slits.
- Method for plotting crossection, 2D & 3D data
